{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回\"夜迷蒙\"主要讲述公孙太夫人与紫藤花在帐篷中对峙的故事。公孙太夫人以一招无形无影的\"六杀\"瞬间击毙饱州六妖，展示了深不可测的武功。紫藤花以毒豆暗算李坏未果，李坏装死后苏醒，以精妙手法反制紫藤花。铁银衣揭露公孙太夫人的真实身份——她的丈夫公孙无胜（公孙败）是一个一生从未胜过一次的绝顶高手，这让铁银衣深感震撼。李坏与公孙无胜在帐篷外的枯白杨树上对饮，公孙透露自己一生只出手四次、每次都败给潇湘神剑、钟二先生、饱宝雪剑、还玉公子这四大高手，原因是\"人错了\"而非武功不足。本章展现了命运的无奈与高手的悲凉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "谢谢，你对我们的夸赞，我们一定会永远牢记在心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下说的只不过是实情而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我也可以向阁下保证，阁下说的一点都没有错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以保证李坏先生在今晨日出之前绝不会死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "太夫人说的话，在下绝对相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "这位女士真的就是公孙太夫人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "大概是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "可是她看起来实在不像，太夫人的年纪怎么会这么轻？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "太夫人说出来的话怎么会这么样不负责任？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "你说我年轻，我实在不敢当。你说我不负责任，我也承担不起。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "我的契约是要在日出时取他的性命，日出前他当然绝不会死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "就算他已经死了，我也会让他再活回来一次，然后再死在我手里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "公孙太夫人，现在我真的佩服你。你这一招六杀，出于无形无影，我相信大概很少有人能看得出我这六个小怪物是怎么死在你手里的。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "不敢当。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "让人看不懂的招式，总是让人不能不佩服的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以等太夫人魂归九天之后，每年今天我一定以香花祭酒，来纪念太夫人的忌辰。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "不敢当。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "只可惜明年今日好像我还没有死，就好像李坏先生还没有死一样。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你真的相信你还能救活他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "用不着我来救活他，如果他真的死了，也没有人能救得活他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "那么你难道认为他还没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "如果你认为李坏先生现在已经真的死了，那么你就实在太不了解李先生这个人了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "如果李坏先生真的会死在你那么样一颗小小的豆子下，那么李坏先生就不是李坏先生了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "这是你的豆子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "我还给你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "其实我也应该想得到，像李先生这么聪明的人，当然不会把这种不容易消化的东西真的吃下去。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "只不过我还是没想到李先生装死的本事居然这么高明。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "那是我从小就练出来的，我偷了别人的东西吃，别人要打死我，我就先装死。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "他说，一个从小就没饭吃的野孩子，总得要先学会一点这一类的本事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "以后每当遇到这一类的情况，我也改不了这种毛病。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "等到这个野孩子长大后又练成某一些神奇的内功时，装死的本事当然也就更高了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "这一点我倒也不敢妄自菲薄，装死如果装得不像，怎么能骗得过紫夫人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "李先生，我真的很佩服你，也很喜欢你，我相信你心里大概也很喜欢我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "老实告诉你，像你这样的女人，我想不喜欢你都不行。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "那么我能不能求你为我做一件事。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
      "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你能不能为我真的死一次？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "李先生，你真是了不起，连我都不能不佩服你。",
      "tone": "佩服",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "不敢当。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你究竟是用什么法子把她制住？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我只不过在她来拿我手里这颗豆子的时候，偷偷的用我的小指尖，在她掌缘上的一些小穴道旁边，轻轻地扫了一下而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以说过了两句话之后，她的这只手就忽然变得麻木了，当然就不能再出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "现在她的右半边身子，是不是已经完全麻木了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "大概是这个样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "所以你也不必再出手了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "李先生，不是我恭维你，你手上功夫之妙，放眼天下，大概也找不出三个人能比得上你的。",
      "tone": "佩服",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "找不出三个人，两个人总是找得出来的，太夫人是不是这两个人其中之一？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "如果我说是你一定不信，如果我说不是你也一定不信。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我相信是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你愿不愿意一个人陪我出去？",
      "tone": "低沉",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "我愿意。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "求求你，千万不要这样子，这样子会让别人笑话的，公孙太夫人留给你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "就让我跟这位老先生出去走走行不行？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我相信我没有看错，我相信你一定就是公孙太夫人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "铁总管，你不会看错，什么人你都不会看错的，否则你怎么能维护李老先生的安全至今？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "那么刚才那位老先生呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "他是我的丈夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "他在他的家族里辈分很高，所以我才会被称为公孙太夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "公孙？太夫人？公孙家族？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "怎么我从来都没有听说过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "因为这个家族现在已经只剩下我先生一个人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "江湖人都知道我这一生中从来没有失败过一次，可是我的先生这一生中，却从来没有胜过一次。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "从来都没有？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "从来没有。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "有些人好像命中注定就是个失败的人，不管他怎么骄，怎么傲，怎么强，可是他注定了命中就要失败。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我可不可以说一句话？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我可不可以问那位老先生的大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "你当然可以问，只可惜我说出来你也不会知道的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "他的名字叫无胜。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "text": "公孙无胜？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "是的，公孙无胜。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "我一点都没法子帮助他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_tai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "公孙太夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "因为他天生就是这么样一个人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "二少爷，这一出戏，你好像已经演完了，好像已经应该轮到我了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "轮到你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "轮到你干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "轮到我杀人，或者轮到我死。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "杀人和死，本来就好像一枚银币的正反两面一样，无论是正是反，都还是同样的一枚银币。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "所以现在是生是死都已经跟你全无关系。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "这不关我的事关谁的事？我求求你好不好，你这一次能不能不要来管我的闲事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "老庄主要我带你回去，我就得带你回去。要你死的人，就得先让我死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "如果你死了，岂非还是一样没法子带我回去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "那么我先死，你再死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我相信你应该明白我的意思，所以你暂时最好还是退下去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_qing_yi_shang_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "淡青衣裳女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好极了，我从来也没有看过你们这样的男人，如果你们真的全都死了，我也陪你们死。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么有这么多人都想死呢？其实我们谁都不必要死。",
      "tone": "轻松",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "只要你能看住那位拉胡琴的老先生的手，我保证我们都不会死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "如果这位老先生不出手，那么我相信这位公孙太夫人到现在为止最少已经死了十七八次了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我们出去走一走好不好？",
      "tone": "低沉",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你愿不愿意陪我出去走一走？",
      "tone": "低沉",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你有没有发现这种酒有点怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "我不但觉得酒有点怪，你这个人好像更怪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你是不是想到我会忽然把你请来，请到这么样一个破地方来喝这种破酒？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "我想不到，可是我来了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "虽然我明明知道你要杀我，我还是来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我是个怪人，可是你更绝，不但人绝，聪明也绝顶。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "所以你当然也明白，我叫你出来，是因为我早就已经看出了我那个老太婆绝不是你的对手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "可是我相信有一点你是绝对不知道的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我找你出来另外还有一个非常非常特别的理由。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你知不知道我的名字？你知不知道我是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我姓公孙，名败，号无胜。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "公孙败？公孙无胜？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "这真的是你的名字？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "真的，因为我这一生中与人交手从未胜过一次。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "公孙先生，公孙无胜先生。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "你这一生中真的从来没有胜过一次？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "我不信，我死也不信。就算把我的脑袋砍下来当夜壶，我也不信。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "我是个坏蛋，是个王八蛋，我是猪。所以我没有吃过猪肉，可是我看过猪走路。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "所以我最少总看得出你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你看得出我什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "如果在江湖中还有六十年前治兵器谱的那位百晓生，如今再治兵器谱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "那么公孙先生你的这一双手绝对不会排名在五名之外。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "那么你怎么会从未胜过。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你看对了，可是你又看错了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你看对了我的武功，却看错了我这个人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我的武功确实不错，确实可以排名当今武林中很有限的几个高手之间。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "如果我，我要找当今江湖中那二十八位号称连胜三十次以上的高手去决一胜负，也许我连一次都不会败。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "那么你为什么一直都败？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为我的武功虽然不错，可是我的人错了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "错在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你知不知道我这一生中只和别人交手过几次？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "几次？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "四次。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "四次？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "公孙先生，以你的武功，以你的性格，以你的脾气，你这一生中只出手过四次？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我战四次败四次。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "如果我要你举出当今天下的五大高手，你会说是哪五个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "武当名宿钟二先生，少林长老无虚上人，虽然退隐已多年，武功之深浅无人可测，但是我想江湖中也没有人能够否定他们的武功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "昔年天下第一名侠小李探花的嫡系子孙李曼青先生，虽然已有二十年未曾出手，甚至没有人能够见得到他一面，可是李家嫡传的飞刀，江湖中大概也没有人敢去轻易尝试。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "小李飞刀，例不虚发。小李探花的侠义之名，至今犹在人心。",
      "tone": "敬佩",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "对曼青先生我一直是极为敬仰佩服的。",
      "tone": "敬佩",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "潇湘神剑，饱宝雪剑，第三代的飞剑客还玉公子。这三个人的剑法就没有人能分得出高下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "他们三位又都是生死与共的朋友，绝不会去争胜负，所以谁也没法子从他们三个人之中举出是哪两个比较更强。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你说得对。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "他们三位之中，只要能战胜其中一位，就已不虚此生。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "这几位你都见过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我不但见过，而且还曾经和其中四位交过手。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "是哪四位？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "潇湘、钟二、饱宝、还玉。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "text": "你选的这四位对手真好，你为什么不去选别的人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_wu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "公孙无胜",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为我这个人错了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    }
